<div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 lesson-instructions">
  <h2>What you need to know before you upload your video!</h2>
  <br />
  <ul class="info">
    <li>Upload a video from your iphone or ipad or desktop</li>
    <li>If using Samsung phone, make sure your video is MP4 format first before uploading!</li>
    <li>Submit a video of a swing that is FACE ON or DOWN THE LINE (Examples below)</li>
    <li>Be sure to give a description of what you struggle with (CAPTION)</li>
    <li>Once you submit a video I will take a look at it and create a lesson for you to view!</li>
    <li>Lessons will be available in 24 hours and will be viewable on the <%= link_to 'VIDEO LESSONS', lessons_path %> page</li>
    <li>Videos are evaluated with <a href="https://www.hudl.com/products/technique" target="_blank">Hudl Technique</a> (formerly Ubersense)</li>
  </ul>
</div>
